columns.title: Jira Sync
columns.formula: =IF(Summary@row = true, "", IF([Sync to Jira]# = false, false, IF(OR(Tasks@row = "Amazon Launch Tasks", PARENT(Tasks@row) = "Amazon Launch Tasks"), false, true)))

columns.title: Child Projects
columns.formula: =IF(Summary@row = true, false, IF({Child Projects} > 0, true, false))

columns.title: Actual Inject LoE
columns.formula: =IF(Summary@row = true, "", IF([Child Projects]@row = true, "", IF(Inject@row = true, LoE@row, IF(INDEX(Description:Description, MATCH("Inject", Tasks:Tasks, 0)) = true, LoE@row, ""))))

columns.title: Actual Planned LoE

columns.title: Estimated Inject LoE

columns.title: Estimated Planned LoE
columns.formula: =IF(Summary@row = true, "", IF([Child Projects]@row = true, "", IF(Inject@row = true, "", IF(INDEX(Description:Description, MATCH("Inject", Tasks:Tasks, 0)) = true, "", [Estimated LoE]@row))))

columns.title: Tasks
columns.description: Project Name should match 1:1 with the IVS Roadmap

columns.title: Issue Type
columns.formula: =IF(AND(Hierarchy@row = 0, Team@row = "IVS PMO"), "Project", IF(AND(Team@row = "IVS PMO", COUNT(CHILDREN(Tasks@row)) = 0), "Task", IF(OR(PARENT(Team@row) = "IVS PMO", Hierarchy@row < 2), "Epic", IF(PARENT() = "Story", "Task", IF(PARENT() = "Task", "Task", "Story")))))

columns.title: LoE
columns.description: 1 LoE = 1 Eng Week. Only use numbers. LoE should be >= 1 for a deliverable.

columns.title: Duration
columns.description: Duration measured in days based on a 5 day work week.

columns.title: Quarter
columns.description: Derived from Start/End Date. Linked to the IVS Roadmap. Projects without a quarter are below the waterline.
